## 2. PROVIDER ARCHITECTURE OVERVIEW

**File:** `contributing/provider-architecture.md`

The AI SDK follows a layered architecture with the adapter pattern:

- **Main Package (`ai`)**: Depends on provider specifications and utilities
- **Specifications (`@ai-sdk/provider`)**: Defines interfaces all providers must implement
- **Shared Utilities (`@ai-sdk/provider-utils`)**: Common HTTP and utility functions
- **Individual Providers (`@ai-sdk/<provider>`)**: Implement specifications using utilities and external APIs

